metadata.name: Ether Girl
metadata.description:
A girl obsessed with Ether. The ether symbol was inspired by the first cryptocurrency I know for transactions with NFT.

Originally uploaded on OS, but finally "burned" after I got my FND invite (Big thank you to a great onee-san for the invite). Then, she was moved into FND, because drawing her took quite time, so FND was more suitable for her.
